school_name: Phillips Beth Israel School of Nursing
comments: Prof. Otero is such a nice lady, without sacrificing the quality of the learning experience. She should be a lesson to other professors. You should not have to be scary to ensure that students are learning. Ease up and be more approachable and people will learn more. I just love her. She showed us the ropes and we had a blast at the same time.

school_name: Phillips Beth Israel School of Nursing
comments: Prof. Otero was a terrific clinical instructor and a great nurse. She was not only a great caregiver, but a knowledgebe, amicable, and affable instructor as well. I am happy that I had the opportunity to learn from an exemplar instructor like Prof. Otero.

school_name: Phillips Beth Israel School of Nursing
comments: AMAZING!!! she was really helpful! very very nice.

school_name: Phillips Beth Israel School of Nursing
comments: She is the most sweetest and understanding person in the whole world. Very nice lady. It was a pleasure to have her.
